---
title: Crispy Artichoke & Patatas Bravas Salad with Goat Cheese & Toasted Almonds
description: Patatas bravas is Spain’s most beloved late-night snack. What could be better than crispy fried potatoes with a spicy aioli sauce? We’ve taken the flavors of patatas bravas and transformed them into a virtuous salad, complete with almonds, goat cheese, and juicy tomatoes. Olé!
